name: Jabba's Space Cruiser
Lore: 'Flying fortress of Jabba Desilijic Tiure. Reaches speeds of 800 kph in atmosphere. The crime lord installed hidden gunports as an unpleasant surprise for would-be pirates.',
Text: 'Deploys and moves like a starfighter. May add 2 alien pilots and 6 passengers. Turbolaser Battery may deploy aboard as a ''react.'' When Jabba aboard, moves for free and immune to attrition.',
